==Save Configuration ==
This operation is used to save Configuration.

=== Request ===
 
{| class="wikitable"
|-
| Method || PUT
|-
| Request URI   || 
/configuration
|-
| Request Body(XML format)
|| 
 <?xml version="1.0"
 encoding="UTF-8"
 standalone="yes"?>
 <configuration
 operation="{operation}"/>
|-
|Request Body(JSON format)
||
 {
 "configuration": {
 "operation": "{operation}"
 }
 }
|}
====Description of request elements====

{| class="wikitable"
|-
| Element || Description || Required
|-
| operation || Save configuration.
Valid value: save
Note: The value is case insensitive
|| Yes
|-
|}
